      "section_class": "bg-white py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20",
      "body": "<div class=\"container-edge container-edge--wide\"> <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12\"> <span class=\"pill-eyebrow mb-6\">Specialty Testing Add-Ons</span> <h2 class=\"!mt-4\"> Bundle Testing Into the Same Visit <span class=\"block h2-sub mt-1\">Lower Cost. One Trip.</span> </h2> <p class=\"text-brand-700 mt-4\"> Most specialty tests are added to the same inspection appointment — saving a second visit and a standalone trip charge. See the <a href=\"/testing-and-specialty/\" class=\"text-accent-600 font-medium underline\">specialty testing section</a> for full scope and methodology on each. </p> </div> <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"> <table class=\"w-full text-sm\"> <thead class=\"text-left\"> <tr class=\"border-b-2 border-brand-200\"> <th class=\"pb-3 font-semibold text-brand-700\">Add-on</th> <th class=\"pb-3 font-semibold text-brand-700\">With inspection</th> <th class=\"pb-3 font-semibold text-brand-700\">Standalone</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody class=\"divide-y divide-brand-100\"> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\"><a href=\"/testing-and-specialty/radon-testing/\" class=\"text-accent-600 underline\">Radon testing (48-hour monitor)</a></td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$125</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$150</td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\"><a href=\"/testing-and-specialty/well-water-testing/\" class=\"text-accent-600 underline\">Well water — standard panel</a></td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$225</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$225</td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\">Well water — with arsenic + radon-in-water</td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$325</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$325</td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\">Well water — comprehensive</td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$425</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$425</td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\"><a href=\"/testing-and-specialty/septic-inspection/\" class=\"text-accent-600 underline\">Septic visual evaluation</a></td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$125</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$175</td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\"><a href=\"/testing-and-specialty/termite-wdi/\" class=\"text-accent-600 underline\">Termite / WDI (NPMA-33)</a></td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$95</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$125</td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\"><a href=\"/testing-and-specialty/mold-inspection/\" class=\"text-accent-600 underline\">Mold — visual</a></td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$175</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$225</td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\"><a href=\"/testing-and-specialty/mold-inspection/\" class=\"text-accent-600 underline\">Mold — visual + air sampling</a></td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$325</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$375</td> </tr> <tr> <td class=\"py-3\"><a href=\"/testing-and-specialty/thermal-imaging/\" class=\"text-accent-600 underline\">Thermal imaging</a></td> <td class=\"py-3 font-bold text-brand-900\">$95</td> <td class=\"py-3 text-brand-600\">$150</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <p class=\"text-sm text-brand-500 mt-4\"> Lab fees on water testing are passed through at cost — pricing above is total including lab fees. Title 5 inspections are scheduled with state-certified Title 5 inspectors and priced separately. </p> </div> </div>"
